text: The doctor was very professional and the clinic is hassle free. They are very transparent and understanding. They made sure all goes well and for the procedure to be done correctly. I'd recommend those that seeks help to dropby this clinic!!

I m really surprised about the super good rating this place gets. My experience as a first time user was super different. Felt ero empathy zero care I was in and out in less than 2min. A Gp would probably have done a better job. Only good thing is efficiency for booking.

First chanced upon Haig O&G, and visited them because of their prompt responsiveness to my enquiry and reasonable charges.

Clinic is easy to get to, a short walk from Eunos mrt.

Dr Umesh is a very fatherly, cute and caring physician with many years of professional experience. I feel very safe in his hands.

And his Receptionists Leah and Clinic assistants, nurses work like a family together.

The level of service is like visiting your family physicians whom you know and trust well.
Haig O&G is my choice for all things gynae.

Thank you Doctor and staff.
You guys are the best! :)
One of the best doctor and nurses I have seen. Doctor is like a father figure and am touched by the warmth and care given doctor and nurses. May god bless them
Dr Umesh is a professional and friendly doctor, alongside his staff who are equally as steadfast and dedicated to their work.
